James, four eight states, draw close to God

00:07:29.600 --> 00:07:32.600
and he will draw close to you.

00:07:32.600 --> 00:07:39.600
Yes, Jehovah is allowing once every opportunity to draw close to him as never before

00:07:39.600 --> 00:07:43.600
and he is speaking to them through his inspired word

00:07:43.600 --> 00:07:50.600
